      "claim": "R lies on both angle bisectors of ∠BAC and ∠MON, so ∠BAR = ∠RAC and ∠MOR = ∠RON.",
      "reasoning": "This is exactly the meaning of saying that R is on the angle bisector of those two angles.",
      "facts_used": ["definition of angle bisector"]
